item.title: I need help!
item.dc:creator: @mrrules mrrules
item.description:
@mrrules wrote:

First your going to need to get a source which you can find billions of them in the download section or google for runescape private server source. I would suggest Testscape for your first server since your new to java/coding servers. Or if your looking for a PK server that you don’t want to edit and just put it up and mess around with friends I would suggest pimpscape.

Testscape: http://xc17.ulmb.com/download/rs2priv/TestScape.zip

Pimpscape: http://xc17.ulmb.com/download/rs2priv/PimpScape.zip

(Taken straight from the download list in the download section of the forum!)

Your also going to download the right java which you can find here…

http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

Download the very first one!

Picture:

Once you have done all that you should be done and ready to run your server.

Please read the sticky topics next time cause they explain everything you need to know.
